response.overview: July 26th is the second day of GCW: Homecoming Weekend. The GCW fans will get to see some of their favorites collide in intense and exciting fights. Second Gear Crew will be in action!  Lineup:  Deathmatch  Alex Colon vs Zachary Wentz  Chris Dickinson vs Calvin Tankman  Scramble  Alex Zayne vs Myron Reed vs Blake Christian vs Tre Lamar vs Jordan Oliver vs Jimmy Lloyd  Tony Deppen vs Lee Moriarty  Allie Kat vs Nate Webb  ACH vs KTB
response.title: GCW: Homecoming 2020 Part 2
